'''Paula Cwikly''' is an American [[soap opera]] writer for the [[Daytime television]] serial ''[[The Young and the Restless]]''. She was [[NBC Daytime|NBC Daytime's]] director of daytime programming.
She is a 1982 graduate of the [[University of Dayton]].<ref name="source1">Batz, Bob (4 April 1998). [http://nl.newsbank.com/nl-search/we/Archives?p_product=DDNB&p_theme=ddnb&p_action=search&p_maxdocs=200&p_topdoc=1&p_text_direct-0=0F51B7702F5F3B43&p_field_direct-0=document_id&p_perpage=10&p_sort=YMD_date:D&s_trackval=GooglePM UD GRAD MAKES MOST OF NBC'S DAYTIME], ''[[Dayton Daily News]]'', Retrieved December 11, 2010</ref>
